signatures.name: getIntervalSeconds(milliseconds: integer) integer
signatures.doc: Gets the seconds component of the duration. Expressed as a value between 0 and 59.

signatures.name: getIntervalTotalSeconds(milliseconds: integer) integer
signatures.doc: Gets the number of seconds in duration.

signatures.name: getIntervalMinutes(milliseconds: integer) integer
signatures.doc: Gets the minutes component of the duration. Expressed as a value between 0 and 59.

signatures.name: getIntervalTotalMinutes(milliseconds: integer) integer
signatures.doc: Gets the number of minutes in duration.

signatures.name: getIntervalHours(milliseconds: integer) integer
signatures.doc: Gets the hours component of the duration. Expressed as a value between 0 and 23.

signatures.name: getIntervalTotalHours(milliseconds: integer) integer
signatures.doc: Gets the number of hours in duration.

signatures.name: getIntervalTotalDays(milliseconds: integer) integer
signatures.doc: Gets the number of days in duration.

signatures.name: getIntervalTotalWeeks(milliseconds: integer) integer
signatures.doc: Gets the number of weeks in duration.
